what does dorothea puente have in common with uncle sam the sewer's backed up the year old boardinghouse mistress told people when they complained other times she blamed rats rotting under the floorboards or the fish emulsion she'd used to fertilize the garden she tried to blot out the fetor by dumping bags of lime and gallons of bleach into the yard and spraying her parlor with lemon scented air freshener when guests dropped in but no matter what she tried the stench refused to fade it clung to the boardinghouse like a curse when her boarders started disappearing a concerned social worker tipped off police who made a gruesome discovery seven bodies buried in the garden not long afterward puente appeared in court accused of murdering her tenants so she could steal their government benefit checks and buy herself luxuries ranging from fancy clothes to a face lift this is a story of keeping up appearances dorothea puente tried hard to project a polished exterior with cosmetic surgery and tailored clothes usa absolutely nothing the u s tells the world what they are doing and what they will do then they keep their word Dorothea Puente Sin City Le p__re Goriot Who Shot Mr. Burns? Tea Vlad III Dracula Fancy Crane James Hanratty Leo Frank Upholstery Charles Peace Clothing Tattoo RuneScape quests San Gabriel Valley Yellow Ribbon campaign (Fiji) Friends EastEnders Rais massacre Textile manufacturing The Dalek Invasion of Earth Constitution of the Turkish Republic of Northern Cyprus Similarities between the Bible and the Qur'an The Silence of the Lambs Rathfarnham Knots Landing Japanese toilet Wal-Mart Ten Commandments Joker (comics) Monk (TV series) Columbine High School massacre The Invisibles Kakapo Diaper Sluggy Freelance 2005 trial of Michael Jackson Felis sapiens Beltway sniper attacks Ultimate Spider-Man Toilet humour Bill O'Reilly (commentator) Operation Market Garden Plastic surgery The Coca-Cola Company Lord of Light Marie Antoinette Aerial (dance move) Hemp Pitcairn